title: The Quest For Mega Man's Lost Secret

media:group.media:title: The Quest For Mega Man's Lost Secret
media:group.media:description:
On this bonus episode of the show, we're talking about an interesting story relating to the unfound video game secret from Mega Man 9. Is it real? If it exists, where can we find it? Was Seth Killian just making everything up? Let me know your thoughts down below!
